%adhunā kamalānāṃ tu śṛṇu saṃketam adbhutaṃ// anekākārabhedotthaṃkaḥ// svarūpātmakaṃ paraṃ// kamalaṃ tena vikhyātaṃ trividhaṃ tatra dahagaṃ// \U2
