%yasya manomadhye taspuruṣasya vaco viśvāso bhavati/        yo rājā sadānaṃdarūpo bhavati// \E
%yasya manomadhye satpuruṣavacanaviśvāso bhavati            yo rājā sadānaṃdapūrṇo bhavati   \P
